name: Reebok Run Supreme 3.0  Sneakers BD4784 Black
short_description:
Need more cushion on your next run? Put this feel-good shoe in your rotation and lay down the miles you want. The Memory Tech sockliner's superior cushion combines with a full-height midsole for shock absorption. Flexibility, stability, and breathability round out the performance feel.
Leather and mesh upper for support and breathability
Low-cut design for freedom of motion and quicker transitions
Lightweight foam bottom provides superior comfort
Bold delta branding and pop color details
Forefoot flex grooves for flexibility
Memory Tech sockliner delivers additional cushion
Midfoot straps integrated into the lacing system for a more secure fit

name: Reebok ZQUICK LITE 2.0 Sneakers BD2100 Black
short_description:
High-speed handling matters. You'll feel it when you lace up these ZQuicks and take them for a spin. A lightweight upper locks down the fit, while rubber gives outstanding grip where it meets the road. In between, a flexible midsole cushions and stabilizes each rev of your running stride.
Mesh upper for lightweight breathability
Low-cut design for freedom of motion and quicker transitions
Midsole geometry for shock-absorbing cushioning and controlled handling
3D FuseFrame seamless heel and eyestay for supportive structure
Minimal CRTek high abrasion rubber for durability and traction
Multidirectional underfoot grooves for better ground contact
MemoryTech Massage sockliner molded for all-day comfort

name: Reebok SPEEDLUX 2.0 Sneakers BD5448 Coral
short_description:
Cuando corres, eres feliz. Haz que este momento sea incluso mejor con un calzado elegante y ligero. Este modelo combina materiales transpirables y detalles llamativos para brindarte un look and feel que todos desearán. Pero no creas que son puras apariencias. La rejilla en la zona media del pie asegura el ajuste, mientras que las ranuras flexibles de la zona delantera le brindan mayor flexibilidad.

Capellada confeccionada de varios materiales para soporte transpirable.
Diseño de corte bajo para libertad de movimiento y transiciones más rápidas
Plantilla de EVA para confort
Relieve ligero
Suela exterior de caucho para durabilidad
Ranuras flexibles en la parte delantera del pie para flexibilidad mejorada

name: Reebok YOURFLEX TRAIN 9.0  Sneakers BD4825 Black
short_description:
You don't let anything hold you back, not even your shoes. Take your training to the next level in these featherweight Yourflex trainers. This sneaker comes equipped with the lightest and most flexible sole in our training line, meaning you can tackle any workout without extra weigh-down.
Neoprene and mesh upper for sculpted comfort and breathability
Low-cut design for ankle mobility
Microweb technology for midfoot support
Oversized delta logo on the side
Ultralight outsole for maximum flexibility
